OL,3,CHundreds of bus drivers set to walk
OL,4,Cout over a pay dispute
OL,6,FHundreds of bus drivers are set to
OL,7,Fwalk out in a series of strikes over a
OL,8,Fpay dispute.
OL,10,F500 workers from Stagecoach in
OL,11,FLiverpool will walk out from 5-8 and
OL,12,F12-15 July, with the threat of a
OL,13,Fcontinuous strike if the row is not
OL,14,Fresolved, said Unite.
OL,16,FThe union said there was imbalance in
OL,17,Fthe pay members receive and the
OL,18,Fdrivers employed by another bus
OL,19,Fcompany - Arriva.
