OL,3,CHundreds of bus drivers set to walk
OL,4,Cout over a pay dispute
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "For too long, Stagecoach has
OL,8,Fgot away with paying its Liverpool
OL,9,Fdrivers on the cheap.
OL,11,F"This shows a total lack of respect
OL,12,Fand appreciation for its workers,
OL,13,Fwithout whom there would be no bus
OL,14,Fservice, and for the communities on
OL,15,FMerseyside who rely on their buses.
OL,17,F"Unite's Liverpool Stagecoach members
OL,18,Fhave their union's total backing in
OL,19,Fstriking for a fair pay rise."
