OL,3,CHundreds of bus drivers set to walk
OL,4,Cout over a pay dispute
OL,6,FMatt Davies, managing director of
OL,7,FStagecoach Merseyside and South
OL,8,FLancashire said: "We offer a
OL,9,Fcompetitive pay and benefits package.
OL,11,F"Claims that our drivers are on #1.40-
OL,12,Fan-hour less than Arriva doesn't tell
OL,13,Fthe full story, as it compares our pay
OL,14,Frate before the 6.4% rise we have
OL,15,Foffered with Arriva after their pay
OL,16,Frise.
OL,18,F"In addition, we pay our Gillmoss
OL,19,Fdrivers additional time each day,
OL,20,Fworth 26p-an-hour on the headline rate.
