OL,3,CHundreds of bus drivers set to walk
OL,4,Cout over a pay dispute
OL,6,F"We also offer better matching of
OL,7,Fstaff pension contributions, and
OL,8,Fenhanced maternity & paternity pay, so
OL,9,Fcomparing the headline pay rate tells
OL,10,Fonly half the story.
OL,12,F"I am sorry for the disruption that
OL,13,Fthis strike will cause our customers
OL,14,Fand we are committed to finding a
OL,15,Fsustainable solution to this dispute."
